{"word":"Rising","slug":"rising","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Rising</b> Rising early<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=15'>Pro 31:15</a> <br/> - For devotions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=5&verse=3'>Psa 5:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=59&verse=16'>Psa 59:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=63&verse=1'>Psa 63:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=88&verse=13'>Psa 88:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=7&verse=12'>Son 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=26&verse=9'>Isa 26:9</a> <br/> - Practiced by the wicked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=27&verse=14'>Pro 27:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=2&verse=1'>Mic 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=3&verse=7'>Zep 3:7</a> <br/> - Practiced by drunkards<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=11'>Isa 5:11</a> <br/> - Illustrates spiritual diligence<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=13&verse=12'>Rom 13:12</a><br/><a href='S:Industry'>Industry</a> <br/> Instances of those who practiced rising early:<br/> - Lot<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=23'>Gen 19:23</a> <br/> - Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=27'>Gen 19:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=14'>Gen 21:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=3'>Gen 22:3</a> <br/> - Isaac<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=31'>Gen 26:31</a> <br/> - Abimelech<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=8'>Gen 20:8</a> <br/> - Jacob<br/> <a hre